<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_137" id="67v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_137_r1l1"><expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Leẅcʒmanſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l2">Pfleger ʒu Helffemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_137_r1l3"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenſt . <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von geleyts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l4"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Nu ſchreıbt Jr vns etwas frem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l5">dıklıch . nach dem Jr vns vormals <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l6">vormals geleyt bey vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd nıht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſo wıſſen wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l7">auch noch ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch auch niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> ʒuſchıken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l8">denn guts Vnd ob Jr Jn <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſtat meynt ʒureıten vnd geleyts <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> begert . ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtee</expan> wır noch niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> / denn daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_line_1572955512427_360">es da mıt / mıt eẅch bey vns <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſol <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> als mıt <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l12"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> wan <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gewonheıt nıht ıſt / geleyt v̈ber lande an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l13"><expan>cʒuſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex>ıs</expan> baptıſte </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_137" id="67v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Lewczmanstein, pfleger zu Helffemberg
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienst. <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von geleyts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu schreibt ir uns etwas fremdiklich, nachdem ir uns vormals
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht
                            <expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> und wir ewch vormals geleyt bey uns
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. So wissen wir auch noch zu disen
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch auch niht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> zu schiken
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts. Und ob ir in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> stat meynt zu reiten und geleyts
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex></expan> begert, so
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stee</expan> wir noch niht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, denn daz es damit mit ewch bey uns
                                <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> sol <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
                        als mit <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>, wan <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gewonheit niht ist, geleyt über lande
                        an<expan>czuschreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex>is</expan> baptiste.</ab>
</div>
